text.tspan: Oop! We're sorry! But you apear to be using an older version of the game! In order to play online,
you need to update your game. To do this, please open BTJW Internet Update. You will need your
activation code ready. Then, the update will begin automatically. Sorry if you want to intentionally
play on an older version, but in order to keep the online mode secure, that is not possible. Sorry!!!
